description: This file defines the 'FriendRequest' model class and associated 'FriendRequestStatus' enum for managing friend request data within the project. It includes properties for request identification, sender and receiver user IDs, status, timestamps, and navigation properties.

classes.name: FriendRequest
classes.description: Represents a friend request between two users, including metadata like status and timestamps, with foreign key relationships to user entities.

classes.name: FriendRequestStatus
classes.description: Enumeration defining possible statuses for a friend request: Pending, Accepted, Rejected.
